  <summary date="2021-01-19T22:11:46Z" status="Introduced in House">Social Services Pandemic Disaster Relief Act

This bill appropriates funding for states, tribes, and localities to administer emergency services and provide short-term, non-cash, in-kind relief to certain disadvantaged children, families, and households to address the COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) emergency.</summary>
